{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775816199311,"sessionID":"ses_2891d7ce7ffeWrz5twmBqnJUqZ","part":{"id":"prt_d76e4cad8001m0UH7b6R8Gx1Tc","messageID":"msg_d76e4b202001YBcZa7k9QoEh5z","sessionID":"ses_2891d7ce7ffeWrz5twmBqnJUqZ","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_be0b9f774c5544db972120dd","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/specs/test_spec.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/specs/test_spec.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AgentCube 测试用例规范 (TDD Specification)\n2: \n3: 要求 AI 在实现业务代码时，同步完成以下测试用例，作为实现完成度的判定标准。\n4: \n5: ## 1. 核心控制器测试 (Workload Manager)\n6: - **TestCase-WM-001**: 验证 Sandbox 创建接口。输入合法 `AgentRuntime` 定义，预期返回 `200 OK` 及 `sessionId`。\n7: - **TestCase-WM-002**: 验证 Sandbox 幂等性。相同 `name` 连续调用两次，预期返回相同 `sessionId`。\n8: - **TestCase-WM-003**: 验证非法输入拦截。输入缺失 `podTemplate` 的请求，预期返回 `400 Bad Request`。\n9: \n10: ## 2. 路由与会话测试 (Router)\n11: - **TestCase-RT-001**: 验证 Auth 拦截。未携带 Bearer Token 请求 `/v1/execute`，预期返回 `401 Unauthorized`。\n12: - **TestCase-RT-002**: 验证会话路由。模拟 Redis 中存在会话，Router 成功将请求转发至后端（Mock 后端）。\n13: - **TestCase-RT-003**: 验证会话过期。模拟 Redis 中 Token 已失效，返回 `404 Not Found`。\n14: \n15: ## 3. 存储层测试 (Store)\n16: - **TestCase-ST-001**: Redis Set/Get 验证。成功存储并检索 `SessionInfo` 结构体。\n17: - **TestCase-ST-002**: 过期时间验证。验证 Key 携带正确的 TTL（默认 24h）。\n18: \n19: ## 4. 编码执行引擎测试 (PicoD)\n20: - **TestCase-PD-001**: Python 代码执行。发送 `print(\"hello\")`，预期 stdout 为 `hello\\n`，exitCode 为 0。\n21: - **TestCase-PD-002**: 错误处理。发送语法错误代码，预期 stderr 包含 `SyntaxError`。\n22: \n23: ## 5. Python SDK 测试\n24: - **TestCase-SDK-001**: 上下文管理器验证。使用 `with CodeInterpreterClient(...) as client:` 确保结束时自动调用 `close()`。\n25: - **TestCase-SDK-002**: 异常映射。服务端返回 500 时，SDK 抛出自定义 `AgentCubeError` 而非原始 HTTP 错误。\n26: \n27: ## 实施要求\n28: - **Go 代码**：必须位于对应的 `*_test.go` 中，可通过 `go test ./...` 运行。\n29: - **Python 代码**：必须位于 `tests/` 目录或 `test_*.py` 文件中，可通过 `pytest` 运行。\n\n(End of file - total 29 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AgentCube 测试用例规范 (TDD Specification)\n\n要求 AI 在实现业务代码时，同步完成以下测试用例，作为实现完成度的判定标准。\n\n## 1. 核心控制器测试 (Workload Manager)\n- **TestCase-WM-001**: 验证 Sandbox 创建接口。输入合法 `AgentRuntime` 定义，预期返回 `200 OK` 及 `sessionId`。\n- **TestCase-WM-002**: 验证 Sandbox 幂等性。相同 `name` 连续调用两次，预期返回相同 `sessionId`。\n- **TestCase-WM-003**: 验证非法输入拦截。输入缺失 `podTemplate` 的请求，预期返回 `400 Bad Request`。\n\n## 2. 路由与会话测试 (Router)\n- **TestCase-RT-001**: 验证 Auth 拦截。未携带 Bearer Token 请求 `/v1/execute`，预期返回 `401 Unauthorized`。\n- **TestCase-RT-002**: 验证会话路由。模拟 Redis 中存在会话，Router 成功将请求转发至后端（Mock 后端）。\n- **TestCase-RT-003**: 验证会话过期。模拟 Redis 中 Token 已失效，返回 `404 Not Found`。\n\n## 3. 存储层测试 (Store)\n- **TestCase-ST-001**: Redis Set/Get 验证。成功存储并检索 `SessionInfo` 结构体。\n- **TestCase-ST-002**: 过期时间验证。验证 Key 携带正确的 TTL（默认 24h）。\n\n## 4. 编码执行引擎测试 (PicoD)\n- **TestCase-PD-001**: Python 代码执行。发送 `print(\"hello\")`，预期 stdout 为 `hello\\n`，exitCode 为 0。","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"specs/test_spec.md","time":{"start":1775816199304,"end":1775816199310}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775816199927,"sessionID":"ses_2891d7ce7ffeWrz5twmBqnJUqZ","part":{"id":"prt_d76e4cd3e0018GjBTIhGQSAG4M","messageID":"msg_d76e4b202001YBcZa7k9QoEh5z","sessionID":"ses_2891d7ce7ffeWrz5twmBqnJUqZ","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_f4d2a85405e846d0a7e9e6fa","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/specs/project.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/specs/project.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AgentCube — OpenSpec Project Context\n2: \n3: > Source: [github.com/ShijunDeng/agentcube](https://github.com/ShijunDeng/agentcube)\n4: > Generated: 2026-03-21 (from source tree reverse-engineering)\n5: \n6: ## Purpose\n7: \n8: AgentCube is a Kubernetes-native sandbox orchestration platform for AI agents.\n9: It provisions isolated sandbox pods on demand, routes HTTP traffic to them through\n10: session-aware proxies, and manages their lifecycle (creation, expiry, idle cleanup).\n11: \n12: ## Tech Stack\n13: \n14: | Layer | Technology |\n15: |-------|-----------|\n16: | Language (server) | Go 1.24, module `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube` |\n17: | Language (CLI/SDK) | Python ≥3.10 |\n18: | HTTP framework | Gin (Go), Typer (Python CLI), FastAPI (example) |\n19: | Kubernetes | CRDs (`runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1`), controller-runtime, `sigs.k8s.io/agent-sandbox` |\n20: | Storage | Redis (go-redis/v9), Valkey (valkey-go) |\n21: | Auth | JWT RS256 (golang-jwt/v5), K8s TokenReview |\n22: | Packaging | Helm 3, multi-stage Docker, GitHub Actions CI/CD |\n23: | Docs | Docusaurus 3.x |\n24: \n25: ## Architecture\n26: \n27: ```\n28: Client / SDK / CLI\n29:   → Router (Deployment :8080)\n30:      ↔ Redis/Valkey (session store)\n31:      → WorkloadManager (Service :8080)\n32:         ↔ Redis/Valkey\n33:         → K8s API: CRDs, Sandbox, Pod, Secret, TokenReview\n34:   Sandbox Pods (with optional PicoD daemon)\n35:   Agentd (idle cleanup controller)\n36:   Optional: Volcano vc-agent-scheduler\n37: ```\n38: \n39: ## Conventions\n40: \n41: - Go packages under `pkg/`, binaries under `cmd/`\n42: - Python CLI at `cmd/cli/`, SDK at `sdk-python/`\n43: - JSON tags use camelCase; Go structs use PascalCase\n44: - K8s resources use `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh` API group\n45: - Normative language: SHALL = mandatory, SHOULD = recommended, MAY = optional\n\n(End of file - total 45 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AgentCube — OpenSpec Project Context\n\n> Source: [github.com/ShijunDeng/agentcube](https://github.com/ShijunDeng/agentcube)\n> Generated: 2026-03-21 (from source tree reverse-engineering)\n\n## Purpose\n\nAgentCube is a Kubernetes-native sandbox orchestration platform for AI agents.\nIt provisions isolated sandbox pods on demand, routes HTTP traffic to them through\nsession-aware proxies, and manages their lifecycle (creation, expiry, idle cleanup).\n\n## Tech Stack\n\n| Layer | Technology |\n|-------|-----------|\n| Language (server) | Go 1.24, module `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube` |\n| Language (CLI/SDK) | Python ≥3.10 |\n| HTTP framework | Gin (Go), Typer (Python CLI), FastAPI (example) |\n| Kubernetes | CRDs (`runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1`), controller-runtime, `sigs.k8s.io/agent-sandbox` |\n| Storage | Redis (go-redis/v9), Valkey (valkey-go) |","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"specs/project.md","time":{"start":1775816199921,"end":1775816199926}}}}
